trans-unit.source: Creates and maintains the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Activities.Description.EtwTrackingBehavior"></xref> sub-element in the service behaviors section of a Sql workflow configuration file.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter og opprettholder det <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Activities.Description.EtwTrackingBehavior"> </xref> underelementet i service virkemåter-delen av konfigurasjonsfilen Sql arbeidsflyten.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Activities.Description.EtwTrackingBehavior> object contains settings to control event tracking behavior in a workflow application.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Activities.Description.EtwTrackingBehavior>objektet inneholder innstillinger for å kontrollere virkemåte i en arbeidsflyt-programmet for hendelsessporing.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Activities.Description.EtwTrackingBehavior>

trans-unit.source: Creates a new instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Activities.Configuration.EtwTrackingBehaviorElement"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Activities.Configuration.EtwTrackingBehaviorElement"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Gets the type of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Activities.Configuration.EtwTrackingBehaviorElement"></xref> instance.
The type of an event tracking behavior element.
trans-unit.target: Typen for en hendelse sporing virkemåte elementet.

trans-unit.source: Returns a new instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Activities.Description.EtwTrackingBehavior"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Activities.Description.EtwTrackingBehavior"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: An instance of an event tracking behavior object.
trans-unit.target: En forekomst av en hendelsessporing virkemåte objektet.

trans-unit.source: Gets the tracking profile name parameter for the event tracking behavior element.
trans-unit.target: Henter sporingen profilopplysninger name-parameter for hendelsessporing virkemåte elementet.

trans-unit.source: The tracking profile filters for specific event tracking data that the workflow runtime generates.
trans-unit.target: Sporing profilen filtrerer for bestemte hendelsessporing dataene kjøretiden arbeidsflyten.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref href="System.Configuration.ConfigurationPropertyCollection"></xref> of the current event tracking behavior element.

En samling av egenskapene for konfigurasjonen.
